.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: blood-red, fuchsia, amber, lilac, azure
There are 5 different nationalities: american, indian, british, german, pakistani
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, pall-mall, dunhill, havana, cain
There are 5 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, fanta, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, snake, hamster, fish, guinea-pig

1. the american is the person who likes blood-red
2. the indian is the owner of the goldfish
3. the person drinking sprite is the person who likes fuchsia
4. the british is the person drinking 7up
5. the person who likes fuchsia is to the right of the person who likes amber
6. the blend-smoker is the owner of the guinea-pig
7. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who likes lilac
8. the person drinking fanta is in the middle
9. the german is on the far left
10. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the snake
11. the pall-mall-smoker is to the left or right of the owner of the fish
12. the havana-smoker is the person drinking iced-tea
13. the pakistani is the cain-smoker
14. the german is to the left or right of the person who likes azure

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Nationality	|   german	|    british	|     american	|    indian	|    pakistani	|
| Color		|    lilac	|      azure	|      blood-red	|     amber	|     fuchsia	|
| Beverage	|     hot-chocolate	|      7up	|      fanta	| iced-tea	|     sprite	|
| Cigar		|     pall-mall	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| havana	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     snake	|     fish	|     guinea-pig	|     goldfish	|     hamster	|
